{"title":"Readers’ Rides: Yann from Cycles Khelonys Folding 27.5+ Touring Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/cycles-khelonys-folding-27-5-touring-bike/","date":1720219624000,"content":"<p><em>Yann from <a href=\"https://khelonys.fr/\" target=\"_blank\">Cycles Khelonys</a> sent in the folding 27.5+ touring bike the team displayed at this year’s <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/Concours+de+Machines/\" target=\"_blank\">Concours de Machines</a>, winning them third place. Let’s check out the process and final build below…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/12-%C2%A9Crealens.jpg?fit=1200,816&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/13-%C2%A9Crealens.jpg?fit=1200,816&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>We are proud to announce that we ended up 3rd at the Concours de Machines 2024!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/14-photo-%C2%A9sentiers.cc.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" /><img width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>This year the goal was to build the best bikes to self-sufficiently explore the mountains for two days while being able to carry the bike on the train.</p>\n<p><img width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The more we develop technologies, the more we increase our environmental print. That’s why we have offered a fully rigid 27,5+, which lead to a much more reasonable riding style, closer to our environment.</p>\n<p><img width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/4.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img width=\"1600\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/2.jpg?fit=1200,2400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/2.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/2.jpg?resize=1200,1800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/2.jpg?resize=768,1152&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/2.jpg?resize=1024,1536&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/2.jpg?resize=1365,2048&amp;quality=75 1365w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/3.jpg?fit=1200,2400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/3.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/3.jpg?resize=1200,1800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/3.jpg?resize=768,1152&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/3.jpg?resize=1024,1536&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/3.jpg?resize=1365,2048&amp;quality=75 1365w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/15.jpg?fit=1200,2400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/15.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/15.jpg?resize=1200,1800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/15.jpg?resize=768,1152&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/15.jpg?resize=1024,1536&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/15.jpg?resize=1365,2048&amp;quality=75 1365w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>How Does It Work?</strong></p>\n<p>1. Remove the wheels<br />\n2. Unscrew the plugs under the seat stays<br />\n3. Screw the plug in the rear spindle location and wrap the chain around to flat the derailleur cage<br />\n4. Use the small stainless steel plate on the fork to lock the direction<br />\n5. Use the wheel spindles to fix them on both side of the bike by using the threads under the seat stays displayed on picture 2.<br />\n6. Handlebar can be fixed along the fork</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2268\" height=\"4032\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/22.jpg?fit=1200,4032&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/22.jpg?w=2268&amp;quality=75 2268w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/22.jpg?resize=1200,2133&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/22.jpg?resize=2000,3556&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/22.jpg?resize=768,1365&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/22.jpg?resize=864,1536&amp;quality=75 864w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/22.jpg?resize=1152,2048&amp;quality=75 1152w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2268\" height=\"4032\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/21.jpg?fit=1200,4032&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/21.jpg?w=2268&amp;quality=75 2268w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/21.jpg?resize=1200,2133&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/21.jpg?resize=2000,3556&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/21.jpg?resize=768,1365&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/21.jpg?resize=864,1536&amp;quality=75 864w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/21.jpg?resize=1152,2048&amp;quality=75 1152w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/1.jpg?fit=1200,2400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/1.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/1.jpg?resize=1200,1800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/1.jpg?resize=768,1152&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/1.jpg?resize=1024,1536&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/1.jpg?resize=1365,2048&amp;quality=75 1365w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1134\" height=\"2016\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/23.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/23.jpg?w=1134&amp;quality=75 1134w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/23.jpg?resize=768,1365&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/23.jpg?resize=864,1536&amp;quality=75 864w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/19.jpg?fit=1200,2400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/19.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/19.jpg?resize=1200,1800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/19.jpg?resize=768,1152&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/19.jpg?resize=1024,1536&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/19.jpg?resize=1365,2048&amp;quality=75 1365w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/7.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/7.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/7.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/7.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/7.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/7.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/7.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Other Details</strong></p>\n<p>1. Stem cap and compression screw can be reused to align the wheel directly on the bike if a spoke break.<br />\n2. Rear light mount is also a beer opener<br />\n3. Brass plate under the fork dropout to preserve the paint when the wheel is out<br />\n4. Lateral bags can be remove without any tool thanks to the MIK system by Basil<br />\n5. The front stainless gusset prevent the cable from removing the paint<br />\n6. This construction ensure no constraint in the seat tube slot</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/17.jpg?fit=1200,2400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/17.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/17.jpg?resize=1200,1800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/17.jpg?resize=768,1152&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/17.jpg?resize=1024,1536&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/17.jpg?resize=1365,2048&amp;quality=75 1365w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2268\" height=\"4032\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20.jpg?fit=1200,4032&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20.jpg?w=2268&amp;quality=75 2268w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20.jpg?resize=1200,2133&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20.jpg?resize=2000,3556&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20.jpg?resize=768,1365&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20.jpg?resize=864,1536&amp;quality=75 864w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20.jpg?resize=1152,2048&amp;quality=75 1152w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Process Photos</strong></p>\n<p>Here are some in-process photos from the shop during construction.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/9.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/9.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/9.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/9.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/9.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/9.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/9.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<p>Frame: Homemade<br />\nFork: Truss homemade<br />\nBars: 16° backsweep homemade<br />\nRack: Stainless steel homemade<br />\nDrivetrain: Shimano Deore M5100 11v Shimano Deore M5100 11v 11-51<br />\nBrakes: Hope Tech 4 E4<br />\nDiscs: Hope Centerlock<br />\nCranks: Miranda 170mm / 32t chain wheel<br />\nBottom bracket: Miranda<br />\nHeadset: Hope EC34<br />\nRims: DT Swiss M582 Ø27,5 x 40mm ID<br />\nHubs: Hope Pro 5<br />\nSaddle: Brooks C17<br />\nGrips: Herrmans Rib Lock<br />\nSeatpost: Kind Shock Lev Integra<br />\nFront light: Knog PWR 2000Lm<br />\nRear light: Knog Plus free</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p><em>We’d like to thank all of you who <a href=\"mailto:readersrides@theradavist.com\" target=\"_blank\">submitted Readers Rides</a> builds to be shared here at The Radavist. The response has been incredible and we have so many to share over the next few months. Feel free to submit your bike, listing details, components, and other information. You can also include a portrait of yourself with your bike and your Instagram account! Please, shoot landscape-orientation photos, not portrait. Thanks!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cycles-khelonys-folding-27-5-touring-bike/\">Readers’ Rides: Yann from Cycles Khelonys Folding 27.5+ Touring Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"4a348b74904eee5126d7716693aaf049986be90ecd63fc5d91a44ef3167b0aa6","category":"Cycling"}